title: Bug 121682: Exception thrown when exporting data from a table containing highlight/map
description: Description: An exception is thrown when attempting to export data from the attached report.
OB: An exception is thrown when attempting to export data from the table containing a group, a highlight rule, and a map rule in the group row.
EB: Exporting the data from the table should export the data without any exceptions.
SR: To reproduce the bug: 1. Open the attached report. 2. Add a table that contains a group, a highlight rule, and a map rule in the group row. 3. Preview the report. 4. Export the data from the table. The expected result is that the data should be exported without any exceptions being thrown.
